edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:19:45.000Z","msg":"取消立法會功能組別<br />\n<br />\n或<br />\n<br />\n取消DQ參選人或議員嘅無謂條款"},{"pid":"b0055dd53f93360dda57c79670a77f60c3519021","tid":1236144,"uid":172385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"始終要成個政制，由區議會、立法會、財委會到選特首都要改革，確保每一環都係公開透明、公平民主，先可以撐到 2047<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0d29c03f554dfcafad90995676885a54d91902","tid":1236144,"uid":216551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"推"}]}